===Etymology===
From {{der|en|LL.|suspensiō}}, {{m|la|suspensiōnem||[[arching#Noun|arching]], [[vaulting#Noun|vaulting]]; suspension}}, from {{m|la|suspendēre}}, from {{m|la|suspendō||to [[hang up]], to [[suspend]]}}, from {{m|la|sub-||''prefix meaning ‘[[under]]’''}} + {{m|la|pendere}} (from {{m|la|pendō||to [[hang#Verb|hang]], to [[suspend]]}}, from {{der|en|itc-pro|*pendō||to hang, to put in a hanging position}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*(s)péndeti|*(s)pénd-e-ti}}, from {{m|ine-pro|*(s)pend-||to [[pull#Verb|pull]]; to [[spin#Verb|spin]]}}.) Compare {{cog|xno|suspensiun}}, {{cog|fr|suspension}}, {{cog|oc|suspensio}}.

